--[[
    Remote Function Helper v3 — GUI Rewrite
    ──────────────────────────
    Drop-in replacement for the GUI section of Function Helper v2.2.
    Paste this file's content in place of the "GENERATED BY GUI to LUA"
    block in Function Helper.lua (everything from "local Function Helper2 = ..." down
    to the end of the Properties section, just before "-- init").

    What changed vs v2.2
    ─────────────────────
    • Fully hand-written UDim2 layout — no GUI-to-Lua exporter artifacts
    • Remote log entries show typed pill badges (RE / RF / UF) instead of
      colour-only bars
    • Left panel has a live search/filter input
    • Right panel has three tabs: Generated script | Raw args | Call stack
    • Named action toolbar: Copy · Block · Save log
    • Status bar: spy mode, remote count, active/idle dot
    • All window controls are 24 px with hover tweens and tooltips
    • Monospace font (RobotoMono) for the code view
    • UICorner, UIStroke, UIPadding used throughout — no pixel hacks
    • Theme tokens defined once at the top; change the palette here only

    Author: GUI rewrite — exx's original logic is untouched
]]

